snippet.title: The Alliance Alive HD Remastered - Ignite, Unite, & Fight! - Combat & System Trailer
snippet.description:
Learn more @ https://nisamerica.com/games/alliance-alive

Confronting the Daemons that rule over the Realms will be no small task. New skills must be discovered and honed. New tools must be harnessed and mastered. And new bonds must be forged and strengthened. Only then can you challenge the Daemons and reclaim the land!

Available October 8, 2019 for Nintendo Switch and PlayStation 4. PC release date to be announced at a later time.
